{"tid":923223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"作為男人真係要學識快啲放低","createTime":"2018-12-01T05:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T11:11:17.000Z","uid":131605,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4423eba0faf85266954a154a7b6bd6a42c16e690","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"作為一個男人拎得起放得低<br />\n被分手後要係一個月後就重新起步<br />\n我都係啱啱比分手 仲係低潮期<br />\n但係應承自己一個月後重新出發<br />\n女人？一街都係 無必要留戀一個唔愛你既人 唔理你感受既人 <br />\n你要生活得更加好 唔好比佢知道你仲留戀佢<br />\n比返小小尊嚴自己 要走得瀟灑<br />\n<br />\n利申一齊時拋晒成個身出黎 最後無晒錢無左份工無埋個人  但男人就係隨時要東山再起"},{"pid":"aca189cd9c32217fe5d026736546e07a01443c86","tid":923223,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"其實男女都係"},{"pid":"5dcde2fea04f597e7d79f8f91d931e3b6be487d6","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"男人就係愛要愛得徹底 走要走得瀟灑<br />\n我係上一段感情真係輸晒所有野 估唔分手後先見到佢真面目 就算以前佢每日訓係我隔離 我都估唔到佢係咁<br />\n但無必要再留戀佢<br />\n現家要愛自己為下一段感情準備 比下一個更好<br />\n咁就係男人"},{"pid":"65d781c3f8dd6acdb3b22e7f2fb9c6fc2a60ec98","tid":923223,"uid":140590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"女人都一樣"},{"pid":"2cd5a051297e3d288a9264871069cd95e0ad4e0a","tid":923223,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"真係乜都輸哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447e3b95e6d55b2ce04e2b0402b48a3008b956d0","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cd5a051297e3d288a9264871069cd95e0ad4e0a","tid":923223,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"真係乜都輸哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"輸咪輸 又唔係未輸過<br />\n如果一齊緊但佢唔愛 都可以係輸既<br />\n最緊要係輸得起 識得起返身<br />\n如果唔係佢就會覺得佢同你分手係做得啱"},{"pid":"839d0d7284f4a1a004fe90ec57911e0e0936f3bd","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:05:54.000Z","msg":"各位巴打輸都要輸得好睇啊<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"3430ab74df7c7bb27581e86e110141b553ea62ec","tid":923223,"uid":72210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"點解會連份工都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5b0d71d80c4bc385c4013058339460aae13bc8","tid":923223,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得好岩呀 我都知道<br />\n但做到都唔容易"},{"pid":"cf9ee5f43a17b384b2f9640012124a97651277b4","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5b0d71d80c4bc385c4013058339460aae13bc8","tid":923223,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得好岩呀 我都知道<br />\n但做到都唔容易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"我都未完全做到<br />\n但要堅持 化悲憤為力量"},{"pid":"d75afc1975f43086e4a2d8360fd4953bd6d2ab67","tid":923223,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf9ee5f43a17b384b2f9640012124a97651277b4","tid":923223,"uid":131605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5b0d71d80c4bc385c4013058339460aae13bc8","tid":923223,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得好岩呀 我都知道<br />\n但做到都唔容易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"我都未完全做到<br />\n但要堅持 化悲憤為力量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"堅持靠決心"},{"pid":"b68ba599e7e6e7a8169bc9cbc2d54b08fc7bae59","tid":923223,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r